flowchart LR
    OP{control} --> RED[Redact<br/>by id or pattern + PII masking]
    OP --> FT[Forget thread<br/>purge one conversation's facts]
    OP --> DF[Delete fact]
    OP --> CL[Clear scope]
    RED & FT & DF & CL --> PURGE[updates memory.json<br/>AND purges search index]
    PURGE --> VER[append-only version log<br/>reason · actor · hash chain]
